      "body" : "@SatishPatro <code>MathContext</code> has no scale, but you can set the scale on the <code>BigDecimal</code> result, or as a parameter on <code>divide</code>. See <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/63098538/401712\">stackoverflow.com/a/63098538/401712</a>"
