    "body" : "<p>You can do</p>\n<pre><code>a.divide(b, MathContext.DECIMAL128)\n</code></pre>\n<p>You can choose the number of bits you want: either 32, 64 or 128.</p>\n<p>Check out this link :</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://edelstein.pebbles.cs.cmu.edu/jadeite/main.php?api=java6&amp;state=class&amp;package=java.math&amp;class=MathContext\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://edelstein.pebbles.cs.cmu.edu/jadeite/main.php?api=java6&amp;state=class&amp;package=java.math&amp;class=MathContext</a></p>\n"
