    "question_id" : 4591206,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Your program does not know what precision for decimal numbers to use so it throws:</p>\n\n<pre><code>java.lang.ArithmeticException: Non-terminating decimal expansion\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3>Solution to bypass exception:</h3>\n\n<pre><code>MathContext precision = new MathContext(int setPrecisionYouWant); // example 2\nBigDecimal a = new BigDecimal(\"1.6\",precision);\nBigDecimal b = new BigDecimal(\"9.2\",precision);\na.divide(b) // result = 0.17\n</code></pre>\n"
